title: Old World Charm
posting_body: ['Two apartments are available in Minneapolis, near Abbott Northwestern Hospital and the Swedish Institute.', ' These pictures are not the apartment, but they are VERY similar.', 'Same floor plan, same floors, same windows.', 'One is a corner unit on the third floor, and it faces east & north.', ' The second apartment is a middle unit on the first floor, and it faces straight south.', 'Your rent for the corner unit will be $967.95 per month (925 rent and 42.95 for water & trash) and includes heat, water, trash, and recycling.', 'Your rent for the middle unit will be $942.95 per month (900 for rent and 42.95 for water & trash).', 'Natural gas for the oven is with CenterPoint Energy.', ' You will need to establish an accounts with CenterPoint if you want to use the stove, and Excel Energy for electricity.', 'Easy access to downtown and Mall of America.', ' However, a couple of transfers to the U of M are needed.', 'Red oak hardwood throughout.', '  Heated by steam radiators.', ' New energy efficient windows recently installed.', ' You will never be cold.', 'Lots of storage space inside the apartment.', ' A storage closet located in the basement, and the cost for the storage closet is $15/month.', ' Gardening space available in the yard.', ' Compost bins on property.', 'Parking is on street, but there is seldom a problem finding a parking spot.', ' If you own a car, we recommend that you log onto the city, and get a Critical Area Parking permit because parking is restricted.', 'We take very good care of this building.', ' Most tenants have lived here for more than 10-years, and we are all respectful.', 'Resident manager is a former Peace Corps volunteer.', 'The corner apartment is available for September 1st 2022, and the middle unit is available now.', '  Call or text Scott', 'show contact info', ';', 'or Steve', 'show contact info', '(no text) to schedule an appointment.', 'We look forward to hearing from you!']
